    <div class="instructions">
        <h3>Common Issues to Check:</h3>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>File Extensions:</strong> Make sure files end with .html (not .htm)</li>
            <li><strong>Case Sensitivity:</strong> Some servers are case-sensitive. Use all lowercase.</li>
            <li><strong>Hidden Extensions:</strong> Windows sometimes hides .html extensions. Your file might actually be "legalservices.html.txt"</li>
            <li><strong>File Location:</strong> All files must be in the same folder as index.html</li>
            <li><strong>File Content:</strong> Make sure the files aren't empty or corrupted</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

